description:
Sam & Max Hit the Road is an awesome point and click style adventure game that was released in 1993. The crime fighting duo take on a case to return Bruno the bigfoot and Trixie the giraffe girl back to the carnival.

This has always been one of my favorite games and I've been wanting to LP it for a while. With my limited internet this week this game is perfect as a short side series because I can play it offline and the video files are about 1/10 the size of most 3D games.
